(- Escalate to maintenance if the same zone jams three times in one shift after guide and) Tj
0 -14 Td
(debris checks.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Escalate immediately if a diverter fails to return fully or if a manual cycle exposes) Tj
0 -14 Td
(abnormal resistance.) Tj
