(This guide creates useful retrieval opportunities because the correct action depends on) Tj
0 -14 Td
(whether the jam is a physical blockage or a control-state mismatch. Those are easy for a) Tj
0 -14 Td
(person to conflate and good for a RAG system to separate.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(A later benchmark query could ask how many verification cartons to run before the line returns) Tj
0 -14 Td
(to full rate. The answer is specific and easy to cite if chunking preserves the restart) Tj
0 -14 Td
(section correctly.) Tj
0 -14 Td
